{
  "stem": "9538.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there were three Jewish houses [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where the Jews-- the remaining Jews were put into.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't go out before 7:00 in the morning or not until after 7:00 in the evenings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so these were like enforced ghettos, but in the town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That time, already Hitler had brought in Russian cards, all in preparation for the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got special Russian cards with a J on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "J for Jude, for Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And only certain shops were allowed to sell to Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, as we were very well known, farmers would bring us food at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Put it over the fence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the local bakers would send us food-- bread and so on, so much so that my mother was able to make parcels to send to her brothers and sisters who were living in the big towns and under great hardships.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was, morally, very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at that time, physically, not so bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to eat, and we were together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew where we were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew that the uncles were there, and the cousins were there, and the-- my grandmother had died in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Both grandmothers had died in '33.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One in '33, one in '34.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let me--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
